data.description: If you are looking for a meticulously clean, well-maintained, and adorable 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo in a gated community with a great location, come take a look! This updated, spacious, move-in ready 3rd floor unit offers a split floor plan, a neutral design, vaulted ceilings, and a lovely sunroom that offers great natural light. The unit has several ponds nearby, and is a short walk to the clubhouse and pool. It is located close to shopping, restaurants, UNF campus, I95, and 295. If you are looking for a gated condo with low maintenance with a great location, schedule your showing today! CASH or non traditional lending only
